    "Silly Egg is found! ƒ£ƒ£/ easyrift üî•",
    "Best Pet Shop = ƒ£ƒ£/ easyrift üî•",
    "REACH THE LEADERBOARDS USING ƒüƒü/ easyrift üèÜ",
    "SECRETS GIVE-AWAY HAPPENING ƒ£ƒ£/ easyrift üåü",
